OL,3,CHancock: Moving patients from
OL,4,Chospitals to care homes was least-
OL,5,Cworst decision
OL,7,FOn Wednesday, he told the inquiry that
OL,8,Fwhile he did not come up with the
OL,9,Fpolicy to discharge patients from
OL,10,Fhospitals to care homes in the early
OL,11,Fstages of the coronavirus pandemic, he
OL,12,Fboth took responsibility and defended
OL,13,Fthe decision.
OL,15,F"Nobody has yet provided me with an
OL,16,Falternative that was available at the
OL,17,Ftime that would have saved more
OL,18,Flives," he said.
