OL,3,CHancock: Moving patients from
OL,4,Chospitals to care homes was least-
OL,5,Cworst decision
OL,7,F"There are things that we can do now,
OL,8,Fand indeed should have been doing for
OL,9,Fthe last three years since this
OL,10,Finquiry was set up to make sure we're
OL,11,Fbetter prepared.
OL,13,F"But obviously having wracked my
OL,14,Fbrains about it... I still can't see a
OL,15,Fdecision that would have been less
OL,16,Fbad. None of the options were good."
