OL,3,CHancock: Moving patients from
OL,4,Chospitals to care homes was least-
OL,5,Cworst decision
OL,7,FWhen the pandemic hit in early 2020,
OL,8,Fhospital patients were rapidly
OL,9,Fdischarged into care homes in a bid to
OL,10,Ffree up beds and prevent the NHS from
OL,11,Fbecoming overwhelmed.
OL,13,FHowever, there was no policy in place
OL,14,Frequiring patients to be tested before
OL,15,Fadmission, or for asymptomatic
OL,16,Fpatients to isolate, until mid-April.
