OL,3,CHancock: Moving patients from
OL,4,Chospitals to care homes was least-
OL,5,Cworst decision
OL,7,FThe inquiry was also shown an internal
OL,8,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,9,Fbriefing note from March 2020 that
OL,10,Fquestioned whether "this is the right
OL,11,Fthing to do".
OL,13,F"The policy implies that emptying a
OL,14,Fhospital is more important than
OL,15,Fprotecting residential or domiciliary
OL,16,Fcare capacity," it read.
