OL,3,CHancock: Moving patients from
OL,4,Chospitals to care homes was least-
OL,5,Cworst decision
OL,7,F"We're three years into this inquiry
OL,8,Fand I think that the situation has got
OL,9,Fworse not better for when the next
OL,10,Fpandemic hits," Mr Hancock told the
OL,11,Finquiry.
OL,13,FThe Covid-19 inquiry continues with a
OL,14,Ffocus on care homes for the next month.
